#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-BTSReader.md:1
msgid "New `vtkBTSReader` for Engys' BTS (Binary Triangulated Surface) files"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-BTSReader.md:3
msgid ""
"You can now read in .bts files generated by Engys' HELYX and ELEMENTS "
"software. Compared with .stl files, .bts files are smaller and faster to "
"load. The file type also supports multiple solids."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-BTSReader.md:7
msgid ""
"The output of the reader is a `vtkPartitionedDataSet` where each partition "
"is a `vtkPolyData` representing one solid."
msgstr ""
